'''贝克大学'''（{{lang-en|Baker University}}）是一所位于[[美国|美国]][[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]]的私立大学。

==历史==
1858年建立，是[[堪萨斯州|堪萨斯州]]第一所四年制大学，隶属于[[联合循道会|联合循道会]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bakeru.edu/student-life/spiritual-life |title=Spiritual Life |publisher=Bakeru.edu |date=2014-07-01 |accessdate=2015-08-08 |archive-date=2015-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905095503/http://www.bakeru.edu/student-life/spiritual-life |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bakeru.edu/bc-admission/programs |title=Academic Programs |publisher=Bakeru.edu |accessdate=2015-08-08 |url-status=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150811063146/http://www.bakeru.edu/bc-admission/programs |archivedate=2015-08-11 }}</ref>

